latestIgtvVideos.title: I miss my dad, every time I think of my 1st period experience 💚
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
First period is a life-changing experience for all the girls. It can be quite scary for them to experience periods for the first time as many of them aren’t even aware of it. It’s important for them to be prepared for it. Let’s come together to spread period awareness and make period education compulsory at schools. Sign the petition today to bring the change in a girl’s life!
Visit periodofpride.com or give a missed call on 9999671283 to sign the petition.
#PeriodOfPride #EkSwachSoch #MenstrualHygiene #Partnered #WhisperIndia
